Thief.Master.Thief.Edition-R.G.Catalyst


Released: 2014 
Genre: First Person Action / Stealth 
Developer: Eidos Montreal / Nixxes 
Publisher: Square Enix 
Version: 1.1
Publication Type: Repack 
Language: Russian, English, German, French, 
Italian, Spanish, Polish, Czech 
Language: English, Russian 
Tablet: SKIDROW

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS: 

Operating system: Windows Vista / 7/8 
Processor: Intel Core 2 Duo 2 GHz or equivalent AMD 
Memory: 4 GB 
Video: nVidia GeForce GTS 250 or AMD Radeon 4800 
Sound device: desirable 
Hard drive space: 24 GB

DESCRIPTION:

If you desperately need to steal something - you've come to the right place.
In a city full of dangers, there is only one person who is able to perform the most complex order.
In comparison, the cruel Baron Nortkrest pale and his greedy guardian, the mysterious Queen beggars ardent revolutionaries and street dwellers "bottom".
His name is Garrett, and he has mastered the art of breaking and entering.
Plague, war, fighting ... let the rest tremble - and he will steal!

Features Repack

Based on Steam Rip Release from RG Origins ; 
Update 2.0
Nothing cut / no recoded; 
Present DLC: 
The Bank Heist - A bank robbery; 
The Forsaken - bonus level for the test mode; 
Booster Packs - set of equipment for opportunist predator and ghost; 
Installation time ~ 25 minutes;
